data.description: Located in Award-Winning Emmens Preserve at Market Common, this pristine condition two story home is MOVE IN READY. Only steps away from Dolittle Lake, this 4 bedroom 3 bath has multiple upgrades and is in incredible condition. A lovely covered porch welcomes you into the home. Once inside enjoy incredible natural light from numerous windows, beautifully maintained hardwood flooring, an open floorplan with vaulted ceilings and a fireplace in the living area. Upgrades include tile backsplash at the breakfast bar and new stainless steel appliances. A beautifully updated screened porch off the dining area with new tile is perfect for relaxing, entertaining, and enjoying the beautiful weather in Myrtle Beach. The Owner’s suite includes a spacious bath with double vanities, walk-in shower, garden tub, and walk-in closet. The walk in closet has custom made shelving to provide an abundance of storage. Two more bedrooms, one bathroom, and spacious laundry room complete the first floor. Upstairs boasts a bonus bedroom that includes a large walk in closet and a private full bathroom. Gutters and a sprinkler system have also been added to the property to keep your beautiful landscaping in prime condition.  A 2-car garage provides plenty of room for a golf car to transport you to the shops and restaurants in Market Common that are only minutes away!  Located in Myrtle Beach’s Market Common area, Emmens Preserve features a resort style pool, workout facility, clubhouse, and 29 acres of trails, parks, and lakes. Resident amenities include outdoor kitchens, fire pits, putting green, bocce ball court, dog park, fishing pavilions, and tranquil lake views. Market Common is an energetic urban village, full of shopping and dining, a movie theater, and popular outdoor events. Only 2 miles to the beach in a location that you can't beat!!
